    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. Validation evidence demonstrates CFD prediction of NIH within 15% of experimental measurements across the full CPB operating envelope. The model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device under the stated COU.",
